  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Borıng.™ is a boring game about doing boring things.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most games try to be fun and enjoyable. Borıng.™ doesn't.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Borıng.™, you'll face multiple monotonous tasks that will make you quit and put your time into something more productive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’ve read this far, it means you're already interested—so why spoil the rest? Just give it a try.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve got nothing to lose. <strong>You're already bored.</strong></p>",
